text:
I have a situation where the `related_blog_posts` functionality is giving false related articles from other tags (because there are not enough related from the same tag). Is this expected behaviour? any way to force the same tag?
I am suppously filtering by the post tags:
```
{% set tags = content.tag_list|map('name')|join(', ') %}
{% related_blog_posts blog_ids="{{content.parent_blog.id}}", tags=tags, limit=2, post_formatter="relatedFormatter", no_wrapper=true %}
```
